-- Legg Mason's Miller Says U.S. Large Caps `Once in Lifetime' Opportunity
-- Charles Stein
-- 2010-07-21T16:41:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-21/legg-mason-s-miller-says-u-s-large-caps-once-in-lifetime-opportunity.html

          
          
             Legg Mason Inc.’s Bill Miller said
investors have a “once in a lifetime opportunity” to buy U.S.
stocks with large market capitalizations at bargain prices.  
 Miller commented in a letter to investors.  
